item.title: "He wants to know people are fighting for him": Take action for Leonard Peltier w/ Nick Tilsen
item.description: TRN Podcast host Nick Estes welcomes Nick Tilsen from NDN Collective back to the show to discuss Leonard Peltier's upcoming parole hearing and the international coalition fighting to get him released after almost five decades of incarceration... item.title: Episode 357: Beauty and the Feast
item.description: What more could be said about Episode 357 that hasn’t already been said…Well, for one thing, I suppose we must note that Webster’s Dictionary defines Episode 357 as “The Episode that takes place in between Episodes 356 and 358.” Interestingly, this Episode would go on to become one of the many episodes of YKS released for public consumption in the year 2024...
